imdb.title: Magical Girl Raising Project
imdb.plot: A social game entitled 'Magical Girl Raising Project' secretly turns some of it's players into actual magical girls. But when Nabuka city ends up having sixteen magical girls an announcement is made that only eight can remain. Thu...
filmingLocations: Vancouver Film Studios, Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada

episodes.title: Welcome to a World of Dreams and Magic!
episodes.plot: Koyuki Himekawa is a middle school girl who is one of a game named "Magical Girl Rising Project" players. One day, that game's mascot, Fav suddenly tell her that she was elected a real magical girl. She earns her power then feels happy because she yearned to be a magical girl in anime when she was a child.

episodes.title: Collect Magical Candies!
episodes.plot: Fav announces; The administration has decided to reduce the number of magical girls from 16 to 8 in Nabuka city, the magical girl with fewest magical candies loses her power one by one in each week. Magical girls are upset about it.

episodes.title: Update Notice!
episodes.plot: Sister Nana and Weiss Winterprison got chat-logs of Fav and Cranberry accidentally after a sad event. They was shocked by that content, and disclose that logs to magical girls.

episodes.title: Add More Friends!
episodes.plot: Snow White and La Pucelle are attacked by someone who aim for their magical candies.

episodes.title: New Character!
episodes.plot: Sister Nana gropes for a way to settle the dispute peacefully. Her attitudes make Ripple uncomfortable.

episodes.title: Get the Super-Rare Items!
episodes.plot: La Pucelle duels with a surprising magical girl. It will be an unexpected result.

episodes.title: Up Your Friendship!
episodes.plot: Snow White is terrified of persistent approaches from Hardgore Alice.

episodes.title: Sudden Event in Session!
episodes.plot: Swim Swim attacks Sister Nana and Winter Prison, who were in the middle of looking for friends. Winter Prison fights back to defend Sister Nana. Meanwhile, Calamity Mary summons Ripple and Top Speed.

episodes.title: Notice of New Rules
episodes.plot: In an effort to instigate a fight with Ripple, Calamity Mary indiscriminately sets cars on fire along a highway. Snow White and Hardgore Alice arrive at the scene to rescue the innocent bystanders.

episodes.title: Sudden Battle Chances Up!
episodes.plot: A few days after the massive tragedy on the highway, Snow White and Hardgore Alice can be seen tending to each other's emotional wounds. Along with the announcement of the new dropout, a new rule is announced!

episodes.title: Server Down for Maintenance
episodes.plot: Swim Swim, having set her sights on Cranberry, executes a plan to lure her into an ambush. Meanwhile, Ripple decides to avenge Top Speed and seeks out Snow White for information regarding Swim Swim.

episodes.title: File Not Found
episodes.plot: Snow White's explanation falls on deaf ears, and Ripple engages Swim Swim in a fight to the death. Just as Koyuki decides to give up being a Magical Girl, Fav divulges the true purpose of the Magical Girl Raising Project.
